	(10,1,'2015-03-05 20:59:37','2015-03-05 20:59:37','[vc_row el_class=\"clearfix phil-app phil-app-march\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"106\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x500\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-text\"][themestudio_title title=\"Philosophy\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Im not a digital marketer; Im a marketer with digital expertise.I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as thelandscape shifts, to drive current and future goals. <em>The results:</em> laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-text\"][themestudio_title title=\"Approach\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Why Abbot + Water? The name represents my approach  a little bit NYC, a little bit LA. But most importantly, it represents the digital world were doing business in. Digital isnt a NYC thing  its an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"112\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x500\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','publish','open','open','','philosophy-approach','','','2015-03-19 19:24:47','2015-03-19 19:24:47','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?page_id=10',5,'page','',0),
	(11,1,'2015-03-05 20:59:37','2015-03-05 20:59:37','','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 20:59:37','2015-03-05 20:59:37','',10,'http://abbot-water.dev/2015/03/05/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(12,1,'2015-03-05 20:59:49','2015-03-05 20:59:49','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"services-heading\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\" el_class=\"services-march-heading\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"services-march-tagline\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between.</p>\r\nWe work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"services-sections\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\" el_class=\"services-blurb\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. Well marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, coordinating offline and online content, social marketing, technology, media, and communications across paid, owned and earned channels.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Start-Ups\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Creative and scrappy  our specialty when developing brand strategy and marketing for start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, its time to build your brand. Well create br