and. Well create branding, content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together well focus on business development efforts to enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, all with monetization in mind.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"space-holder\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"25px\" el_class=\"services-space\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_text_separator title=\"SERVICES\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\" align=\"align_center\" color=\"grey\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_service_shortcode posts_per_page=\"8\" has_boder=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-autosave-v1','','','2015-03-18 18:07:22','2015-03-18 18:07:22','',12,'http://abbot-water.dev/2015/03/05/12-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(32,1,'2015-03-05 21:50:56','2015-03-05 21:50:56','Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBrands\r\n\r\nConsider us your Digital SWAT team. Well marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPublishers / Ad Tech\r\n\r\nBrand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together well enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStart-ups / Emerging Brands\r\n\r\nCreative and scrappy  our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, its time to build your brand. Well create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.\r\n\r\nServices:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Content Marketing &amp; Distribution</span>: The lines between brands and publishers have never been blurrier, but the issues are clear  you need eyeballs on the editorial content you are creating. Simply put  I help clients craft strategic marketing and distribution strategies that drive engagement with the content you spend time and money creating, then measure the impact of those efforts to the business with solid KPIs.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Video Strategy</span>: How do you navigate a fragmented, cluttered and messy landscape? With expertise and education. Well start with an overview of the video landscape, then move on to tailored navigation of and strategy for video your content and advertising, across devices, platforms and publishers.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Brand Building</span>: Youve got a product, youve got funding. Now you need to build a brand, build awareness, and generate revenue. Ill leverage my billion-dollar-brand marketing experience to develop innovative strategies, materials and content, targeted to your audience, in an efficient and scrappy way, to complement DR marketing and other lower-funnel activities.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Media Strategy</span>: Banners, search, social, video, high-impact, programmatic, mobile  there are many cookie-cutter media plans out there by accident and by design. With a depth of knowledge across online and offline media, I build strategies for effective investment that support, and impact, brand goals.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Ad Product Development &amp; Monetization</span>: As a Publisher or Ad Tech Vendor, Brand Marketer attention, and advertising dollars, can be hard to get! I\'ll leverage my +12-year brand-side career to create marketable and differentiated ad products for you, while unlocking new revenue streams around content, video and native. As the recipient of countless pitches, Ive seen the good, the bad and the ugly. I can help you avoid those last two categories while enriching your selling efforts, creating ROI for brand and agency clients, with monetization in mind.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Communications Planning and Social Marketing:</span> At the intersection of PR, Marketing and Influencers, you need synthesized communications and social marketing planning. Ill help you coordinate across teams, departments and agencies to determine how and where to communicate, with tailored content and a solid amplification plan, both must-haves in the PR and social stratosphere.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Innovation and Emerging Tech</span>:Does your team have a Digital Inspiration Pipeline? How do you operationalize innovation? I curate the emerging tech landscape, providing strategic counsel on relevant trends, while crafting tailored test-and-learn opportunities for brands big and small.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Resource Management:</span> How can you get the most out of your resource and agency partners? As a cross-functional leader, Ive managed teams across agencies, brands and publishers to accomplish projects that can span weeks, months or years. With honed communication skills and detail-focused project management, no team is too big (or too small) to be productive.</li>\r\n</ul>','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 21:50:56','2015-03-05 21:50:56','',12,'http://abbot-water.dev/2015/03/05/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
