	(38,1,'2015-03-05 22:12:54','2015-03-05 22:12:54','<h3>About Heather:</h3>\r\n<p>A results-driven digital brand marketing and media expert, Heather Bergstein has spent over a decade working with global Beauty and Fashion companies including LOreal, Ralph Lauren and Estee Lauder. Heathers career began in traditional marketing, and that remains to be the foundation of her approach; shes not a digital marketer, but a marketer with digital expertise.</p>\r\n<p>As President and Chief Strategist of Abbot + Water, Heather works with brands, start-ups and publishers as a dot connector, cross-functional leader, and digital swat team of one, creating tailored and informed strategies that drive engagement and ROI, built to evolve in an ever-changing marketing landscape.</p>\r\n<p>A passionate digital leader, Heather is a frequent panelist and industry participant with a focus on digital content, video and media strategy; her activities, honors awards speak to her dedication. She is based in NYC, where she lives with her son, and bounces between NYC and Santa Monica (aka Silicon Beach), to stay on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.</p>\r\n<h4>Activities, Honors, Awards</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013</li>\r\n	<li>Editorial Board Member, <em>Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em></li>\r\n	<li>Internet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social</li>\r\n	<li>Member, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014</li>\r\n	<li>Co-Founder, The Cabernet Group</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca</li>\r\n	<li>Upcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015</li>\r\n</ul>','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 22:12:54','2015-03-05 22:12:54','',8,'http://abbot-water.dev/2015/03/05/8-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(39,1,'2015-03-05 22:13:55','2015-03-05 22:13:55','<h3>Philosophy</h3>\r\n<p>Im not a digital marketer; Im a marketer with digital expertise.I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as thelandscape shifts, to drive current and future goals. The results: laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\r\n<h3>Approach</h3>\r\n<p>Why Abbot + Water? The name represents my approach  a little bit NYC, a little bit LA  and it sounds cool. But most importantly, it represents the digital world were doing business in. Digital isnt a NYC thing  its an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 22:13:55','2015-03-05 22:13:55','',10,'http://abbot-water.dev/2015/03/05/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
