	(190,1,'2015-03-12 00:12:26','2015-03-12 00:12:26','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"services-tagline\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.</em></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. Well marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together well enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][themestudio_title title=\"Start-ups / Emerging Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Creative and scrappy  our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, its time to build your brand. Well create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"32px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_text_separator title=\"SERVICES\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\" align=\"align_center\" color=\"grey\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_service_shortcode posts_per_page=\"8\" has_boder=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-12 00:12:26','2015-03-12 00:12:26','',12,'http://abbot-water.dev/?p=190',0,'revision','',0),
	(191,1,'2015-03-12 01:10:43','2015-03-12 01:10:43','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"bio-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"black\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x667\" style=\"vc_box_border\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Heather Bergstein\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"]President + Chief Strategist[/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A results-driven digital brand marketing and media expert, Heather Bergstein has spent over a decade working with global Beauty and Fashion companies including LOreal, Ralph Lauren and Estee Lauder. Heathers career began in traditional marketing, and that remains to be the foundation of her approach; shes not a digital marketer, but a marketer with digital expertise.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As President and Chief Strategist of <strong>Abbot + Water</strong>, Heather works with brands, start-ups and publishers as a dot connector, cross-functional leader, and digital swat team of one, creating tailored and informed strategies that drive engagement and ROI, built to evolve in an ever-changing marketing landscape.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A passionate digital leader, Heather is a frequent panelist and industry participant with a focus on digital content, video and media strategy; her activities, honors awards speak to her dedication. She is based in NYC, where she lives with her son, and bounces between NYC and Santa Monica (aka Silicon Beach), to stay on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][themestudio_title title=\"Activities, Honors + Awards\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013\r\nEditorial Board Member,<em> Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em>\r\nInternet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social\r\nMember, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014\r\nCo-Founder, The Cabernet Group\r\nVolunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca\r\nUpcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-12 01:10:43','2015-03-12 01:10:43','',8,'http://abbot-water.dev/?p=191',0,'revision','',0),
